suppress.notes:
Dependency-Check maps WireMock gRPC extension artifacts 1.0.0-beta.5 to the old WireMock
product line affected by CVE-2018-9116. The framework uses WireMock core 4.0.0-beta.38;
CVE-2018-9116 applies to WireMock before 2.16.0. Re-evaluate when upgrading WireMock gRPC.

